        "content": "<p>Hi, I think that <code>rw [Int.ModEq]</code> may be what you're after.</p>\n<p>Also, this snippet might save some typing in vscode:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s2\">\"zmod\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"s2\">\"prefix\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"zmod\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"s2\">\"body\"</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"s2\">\"[ZMOD $1]\"</span><span class=\"o\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"s2\">\"description\"</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"shortcut for ZMOD\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
